      "comment": "VERACIOUS VAL (1) settled back off the inside but went through her gears strongly to find the frame with a 8 length third (30.60) at Q Parklands in Mix 5. Goes very well from this draw. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 10 starts. Top chance in this line up. RICOCHET RIPPLE (6) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Brunswick Rocket (22.04) in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can measure up. SHIMMERING LIGHT (2) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth at this track, but was among the placings at Q Straight three back. Expecting significant improvement this line-up.",
